2. firstly I will cut the current rectangle into two rectangles
3. there are two ways to cut it i.e. row wise and column wise
4. So, firstly cut it through row state will be dp(cut, col) + dp(row - cut, col) and similarly for column
5. and my base case will be when I reach row length = 1 and column length also 1 then we return price[1][1].
