# Intuition
Keep track of L/R's balance. We cannot transform the source only if:
1) L blocks expected R shifts/R blocks expected L shifts
2) L in source/R in target has no matching pair (balance == 0)
3) At the end of iteration some balance is not 0

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(N)
- Space complexity: O(1)

# Code
```
class Solution {
public:
    bool canChange(string s, string t) 
    {
        int balanceL{ 0 };
        int balanceR{ 0 };
        for (int pos{ 0 }; pos < s.size(); ++pos)
        {
            if (s[pos] == 'L')
            {
                if (balanceR != 0 || (t[pos] != 'L' && balanceL == 0))
                    return false;

                --balanceL;
            }
            else if (s[pos] == 'R')
            {
                ++balanceR;
            }

            if (t[pos] == 'L')
            {
                ++balanceL;
            }
            else if (t[pos] == 'R')
            {
                if (balanceL != 0 || (s[pos] != 'R' && balanceR == 0))
                    return false;

                --balanceR;
            }
        }

        return balanceL == 0 && balanceR == 0;
    }
};
```

