# Approach
We create 2 stacks and fill the stack with start and target. Afterwards we perform some check operations for the question.
The key here is to focus on the order of left and right in start and target. 
The left can appear on leftwards of target as compared to start
Similarlt, right can appear on rightwards of target as compared to start and not vice - versa.
