We count consequitive zeros `(i - j + 1)`.

For each zero, we add `(i - j + 1)` subarrays:
- `0` -> +1
- `00` -> +2 (`_0` and `00`)
- `000` -> +3 (`__0`, `_00`, and `000`)
- and so on...

