# Approach
The problem description needs the total subarrays with only `0`.

This algorithm used `left` and `right`pointers as the starting and ending point of sliding window. We set the window as subarray which only includes `0`. 

To count the total subarrays i have used the formula `right - left + 1` which gives the total subarrays in between `left` and `right` indices.
# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(n)
