*Let say we have 5 consecutive zero.*
*From 5 consecutive zero we can form 5 subarray of size 1*
*From 5 consecutive zero we can form 4 subarray of size 2*
*From 5 consecutive zero we can form 3 subarray of size 3*
*From 5 consecutive zero we can form 2 subarray of size 4*
*From 5 consecutive zero we can form 1 subarray of size 5*

*So for 5 consecutive zero total will be 5+4+3+2+1 = 5*(5+1)/2  no of subarrays*

