*ex-for nums=[0,0,0,2,0,0] there will be 3 & 2 consecutive zeros*
*So for 3 total subarray will be 3*(3+1)/2 = 6*
*So for 2 total subarray will be 2*(2+1)/2 = 3*
*So ans will be 6+3 = 9*

