We will iterate through the array and keep track of length of each contiguous subarray of 0. Then when we get a non 0 number we just calculate the no. of subarrays from the above lengthx ((x-1)/2) and add it to our answer. Then make length 0 again for next contiguous subarrays of 0. Add at last add all occurances of 0s to the answer.
